data.description: Welcome Home! Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath Ranch built in 2021, Open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, large center island. Living room with gleaming hardwood floors, recessed lights. Dining room has slider leading you to your relaxing deck and patio for all your summer cookouts with family & friends, a large beautiful fenced yard, with storage shed. Main bedroom features walk in closet, beautiful tile private bathroom, across the hall you will find 2 more spacious carpeted bedrooms, ceiling fans, 2nd full bathroom. This home has a full basement for storage or a future family room. Keep cool in the summer with central air. Close to YMCA, Wareham Crossing, great highway access. First Showings at Open House Saturday April 6th 11-1pm, Sunday April 7th 12-2pm.
